| Decision | Choice | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| `formatTime` location | `src/lib/time.ts` | Shared pure utility, testable in node environment, importable by both Selector and Chat |
| Header scroll behavior | `position: sticky; top: 0` inside `.chat` | Header stays visible during message scroll without JS; works because `.chat` is the scrolling ancestor |
